text: Kristīne Petrikina (born 13 October 1985) is a Latvian footballer who plays as a defender. She has been a member of the Latvia women's national team. ==References== Category:1985 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football defenders Category:Latvian women's footballers Category:Latvia women's international footballers Category:FK Liepājas Metalurgs (women) players Category:FC Skonto/Cerība-46.vsk. players
